= View Submissions

- Epic: Student Progress Tracking
- Actor: Teacher
- MVP: No
- BR: BR19
- Description / Notes: View all student submissions for an assignment.
- As a: Teacher
- I want to: View student submissions
- So that: I can track performance.
- Trigger: The teacher opens an assignment to see who has submitted.
- Pre-condition:
    - The teacher is logged in.
    - The assignment exists.
- Post-condition:
    - A list of student submissions for the assignment is displayed, along with their submission status (submitted, late, not submitted).
- Solution (Step-by-Step):
  - Go to the course's assignment list.
  - Select an assignment.
  - The list of student submissions is displayed.